><br />15:30 Kanuti Gildi SAAL studio /Pikk 20/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/55/\"><strong>EIKE &Uuml;LEVAIN &amp; K&Auml;RT T&Otilde;NISSON &amp; JAAK SAPAS</strong> &ldquo;Upstairs, Downstairs&rdquo;, 20&rsquo;</a><br /><br />15:30 Teatrilabor /Kaarli pst.9/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/50/\"><strong>P&Auml;&Auml;R P&Auml;RENSON</strong> &ldquo;The Valley of Misery&rdquo;, 50&rsquo;</a><br /><br />17:00 Von Krahl Theatre /Rataskaevu 10/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/62/\"><strong>NELE SUISALU &amp; FLORENT HAMON</strong> /FRA/ &ldquo;Ball&rdquo;, 60&rsquo;</a><br /><br />18:30 theatre NO99 /Sakala 3/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/63/\"><strong>KATRIN ESSENSON &amp; JANE SAKS</strong> &ldquo;Obscure matters&rdquo;, 45&rsquo;</a><br /><br />20:00 KUMU auditorium /Weizenbergi 34-Valge 1/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/64/\"><strong>DANCE THEATRE ZICK</strong> &ldquo;The Hoffmann &ndash; Promenade&rdquo;, 75&rsquo;</a><br /><br />22:00 Kanuti Gildi SAAL /Pikk 20/<br /><a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/event/65/\"><strong>MART KANGRO </strong>&ldquo;Can&rsquo;t Get No / Satisfaction&rdquo;, 75&rsquo;</a></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>NB! You can find the <a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/registration_estoniandanceplatform_2009.doc\"><strong>REGISTRATION FORM FOR PROFESSIONALS</strong></a> here!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>NB! You can find the detailed <a href=\"http://www.saal.ee/6/\"><strong>TRANSFER info to KUMU</strong></a> here!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">DANCE PLATFORM is organized by</span>: Kanuti Gildi SAAL and Independent Association of Dance. <br /><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">DANCE PLATFORM partners:</span> Von Krahl Theatre, theatre NO99, KUMU auditorium, Teatrilabor, bar-club Juuksur.<br /><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Supprted by:</span> Estonian Ministry of Culture, Cultural Endowment of Estonia, Tallinn City Council Cultural Heritage Depart