INSERT INTO `saal_events_en` VALUES (373,'','<p>\"The Drone of Monk Nestor\" is the continuing of \"Chude,\" where the chronicler monk Nestor travels from his cave monastery in Kiev to the shores of Lake Peipsi. There, between golden bulbs, he sees the dancing chude. The monks\' mouth drops down and lets out a primal growl.</p>\r\n<p><br /> The chude dances while the sun sets the glimmering plain into the dark woods beyond its reach. Black as the night, the portentous eagle falls from the blue of the Eastern sky. Claws clinching the ground, his open beak waits for incense and chant\r\n<script src=\"http://www.saal.ee/ohjur/tiny_mce/themes/advanced/langs/en.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\r\n.<br /> <br /> Whilst the woods hold a blue dawn.On a branch sits a giant grouse, like scorched coal with bloodshot eyes. Claws sharp, beak open wide, waiting for the burning song of the children<br /> of Chude. Into the distance the domes ring.<br /> <br /> Choreography/dance: Karl Saks<br /> Sound: Karl Saks, Hendrik Kaljuj&auml;rv<br /> Sceneography: Triin Isak</p>\r\n<p>Producer: S&otilde;ltumatu Tantsu &Uuml;hendus</p>\r\n<p>Light: Revo Koplus</p>\r\n<p>Premiere: March 8th 2011 in Kanuti Gildi SAAL</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.stu.ee\" target=\"_blank\">www.stu.ee</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>[popimg] monk-oh-01.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-02.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-03.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-04.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-05.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-06.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-07.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-08.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-09.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-10.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-11.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]&nbsp;[popimg] monk-oh-12.jpg %% Allkiri [/popimg]</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><em>&#1040;&#1042;&#1043;&#1059;&#1057;&#1058;&#105