00;&#1082;&#1086; &#1084;&#1099; &#1074;&#1077;&#1088;&#1080;&#1084; &#1090;&#1086;&#1084;&#1091;, &#1095;&#1090;&#1086; &#1074;&#1080;&#1076;&#1080;&#1084; &#1085;&#1072; &#1089;&#1094;&#1077;&#1085;&#1077;? &#1050;&#1090;&#1086; &#1089; &#1085;&#1072;&#1084;&#1080; &#1088;&#1072;&#1079;&#1075;&#1086;&#1074;&#1072;&#1088;&#1080;&#1074;&#1072;&#1077;&#1090;? &#1043;&#1077;&#1088;&#1086;&#1081; &#1089;&#1087;&#1077;&#1082;&#1090;&#1072;&#1082;&#1083;&#1103; &#1080;&#1083;&#1080; &#1072;&#1082;&#1090;&#1077;&#1088;, &#1085;&#1072;&#1093;&#1086;&#1076;&#1103;&#1097;&#1080;&#1081;&#1089;&#1103; &#1085;&#1072; &#1089;&#1094;&#1077;&#1085;&#1077;?&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'','<p>August DanceFestival 2011:</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><strong>MART KANGRO</strong> /Tallinn/ <strong>\"Talk To Me\"</strong><em></em></p>\r\n<p>Kanuti Gildi SAAL</p>\r\n</div>');
INSERT INTO `saal_events_en` VALUES (375,'','<p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> Normal   0   21         false   false   false                             MicrosoftInternetExplorer4 </xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> </xml><![endif]--><!--[if !mso]> \r\n<object  classid=\"clsid:38481807-CA0E-42D2-BF39-B33AF135CC4D\" id=ieooui>\r\n</object>\r\n<mce:style><!  st1\\:*{behavior:url(#ieooui) } --> <!--[endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]> <mce:style><!   /* Style Definitions */  table.MsoNormalTable 	{mso-style-name:Normaaltabel; 	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0; 	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0; 	mso-style-noshow:yes; 	mso-style-parent:\"\"; 	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; 	mso-para-margin:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt; 	mso-pagination:widow-orphan; 	font-size:10.0pt; 	font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; 	mso-ansi-language:#0400; 	mso-fareast-language:#0400; 	mso-bidi-language:#0400;} --> <!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p>Pepperminta (Ewelina Guzik) is an anarchist of the imagination. She lives in a futuristic rainbow villa and according to her own rules. Colours are the young woman\'s best friends and strawberries are her pets. She knows the most amazing remedies to free people of their fears. Pepperminta&lsquo;s wish is for everyone to see the world in her favorite colors. Werwen (Sven Pippig), a young plump and shy man yet whose sex appeal Pepperminta finds highly attractive, and the beautiful Edna (Sabine Timoteo), who talks to tulips, join her on her passionate mission.</p>\r\n<p>These three musketeers of a different kind set out to fight for a more humane world. Wherever the gang appears, everything is turned upside down and people\'s lives are transformed in the most miraculous and wondrous of ways.</p>\r\n<p>Pipilotti Rist (b. 1962, Grabs, Switzerland) is a well known video artist whose work has been widely exhibited all over the world and for which she has received many awards. She studied applied arts in Vienna and video in Basel. In 1997 her work was first featured in the Venice Biennial, where she was awarded the Premio 2000 Prize. She was a member of the pop group Les Reines Prochaines. \"PEPPERMINTA\" is her first feature film.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Director: Pipilotti Rist</p>\r\n<p>Cast: Ewelina Guzik, Sven Pippig, Sabine Timoteo</p>\r\n<p>Language: German with English subtitles</p>\r\n<p>Duration: 80&acute;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.pipilottirist.net/\">http://www.pipilottirist.net/</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'','<p>August DanceFestival 2011:</p>\r\n<p><strong>PIPILOTTI RIST </strong>/Z&uuml;rich-Los Angeles/ <strong>\"PEPPERMINTA\"</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cinema S&otilde;prus</p>');
INSERT INTO `saal_events_en` VALUES (376,'','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\"ONE TRIP/ONE NOISE\" is an audio-theatre piece inspired fully by the music of a French rock-band Noir D&eacute;sir (1983-2010). To be exact, by their legendary album \"Des Visages Des Figures\" that was released on September 11 2001(!). For French-speaking world, Noir D&eacute;sir was much more than just another rock-group. It could be compared to cult acts such as Kino in Russia, Eppu Normaali in Finland or Vennaskond in Estonia. Despite of the fact that Noir D&eacute;sir\'s political background and the tragical life of the frontman Bertrand Cantat could provide enough material for an independent theatre production, nu.unioon\'s audio-piece is nothing more than an interpretation of Noir D&eacute;sir\'s music. By four young Estonian actors + one electronic musician. They are the authors of a set audio-journey that reflects the echoes what the music is creating in them.</p>\r\n<p>Any kind of echoes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\"ONE TRIP/ONE NOISE\" is a wild and rocking, yet intimate experience that stands in undefined area of contemporary theatre, contemporary music and rock music.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>There will be ONLY one studio-live that is transmitted to the audience by Klassikaraadio - the most prominent Estonian contemporary and classical music channel. The production can be experienced both on air or via web (also visually) at <a href=\"http://klassikaraadio.err.ee/\">klassikaraadio.err.ee</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A public gathering for listening \"ONE TRIP/ONE NOISE\" is organised at Kanuti Gildi SAAL in the frame of Augusti TantsuFestival 2011 and at Rakvere Theatre.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To experience the LIVE-performance with all your senses, you are welcomed to come to ERR Studio One (Kreutzwaldi 14, Tallinn) on August 18. No admission. Doors from 21.30.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cast: Riina Maidre (Von Krahl Theatre), Gert Raudsep (Theatre NO99), Taavi T&otilde;nisson (Estonian State Puppet and Youth Theatre NUKU), Uku Uusberg (Estonian Drama Theatre) and Taavi Kerikm&auml;e (Improtest, ASK:, ensemble U:).</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Director: Tarmo Tagamets (V&otilde;ru City Theatre, nu.unioon)</p>\r\n<p>Musical Director: Tauno Aints</p>\r\n<p>Orchestra: Erko Laurimaa, Elvis Jakobson, Tarmo Sillaots, Riivo Torstenberg</p>\r\n<p>Language: Estonian with possible (combined) French, English, Russian</p>\r\n<p>Premiere: August 18, 2011 on Klassikaraadio (ERR, Estonian Public Broadcasting)</p>\r\n<p>Producer: nu.unioon</p>\r\n<p>Co-Producers: ERR, Kanuti Gildi SAAL, Rakvere Teater</p>\r\n<p>Supporter: Eesti Kultuurkapital</p>\r\n<p>Sound-engineer: Tarmo Kesk&uuml;ll (Rakvere Teater)</p>\r\n<p>Klassikaraadio live broadcast was brought/will be brought to you by tonmaster/sound engineer Siim M&auml;esalu and producer Marge-Ly Rook&auml;&auml;r.</p>\r\n<p>Duration: 60\'</p>\r\n<p>Free of charge!</p>\r\n<p>nuunioon.ee</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>&#1040;&#1042;&#1043;&#1059;&#1057;&#1058;&#1054;&#1042;&#1057;&#1050;&#1048;&#1049; &#1060;&#1045;&#1057;&#1058;&#1048;&#1042;&#1040;&#1051;&#1068; &#1058;&#1040;&#1053;&#1062;&#1040; 2011</em></p>\r\n<p><em>18.08 / 22:00/ &#1088;&#1072;&#1076;&#1080;&#1086; Klassikaraadio + Kanuti Gildi SAAL + &#1056;&#1072;&#1082;&#1074;&#1077;&#1088;&#1077;&#1089;&#1082;&#1080;&#1081; &#1090;&#1077;&#1072;&#1090;&#1088;&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>nu.unioon</em></strong><em>&nbsp;/&#1056;&#1072;&#1082;&#1074;&#1077;&#1088;&#1077;/:&nbsp;</em><strong><em>ONE TRIP/ONE NOISE</em></strong><em>&nbsp;(&#1072;&#1091;&#1076;&#1080;&#1086; &#1087;&#1086;&#1089;&#1090;&#1072;&#1085;&#1086;&#1074;&#1082;&#1072;) &#1055;&#1056;&#1045;&#1052;&#1068;&#1045;&#1056;&#1040;!</em></p>\r\n<p><em><br /></em></p>\r\n<p><em>&#1040;&#1091;&#1076;&#1080;&#1086; &#1087;&#1086;&#1089;&#1090;&#1072;&#1085;&#1086;&#1074;&#1082;&#1072; &#1090;&#1074;&#1086;&#1088;&#1