rous and catchy documentary explore the effects of bonuses, both emotional and financial, on human behaviour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The Thinking Machine is brought to you in cooperation with the US Embassy in Tallinn.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><a href=\"http://www.plektrumfestival.com\"><span>www.plektrumfestival.com</span></a></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'','<p>PLEKTRUM FESTIVAL 2011:</p>\r\n<div><span>Plektrum kino. Dokumentaalfilm: Freakonomics</span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">reû. Heidi Ewing, Alex Gibney, Seth Gordon, Rachel Grady, Eugene Jarecki, Morgan&nbsp;Spurlock, USA 2010</p>\r\n</div>');
